<i>if he fools around again.</i>

22:31.240 --> 22:33.391
<i>Will he? Will she?</i>

22:33.600 --> 22:37.674
<i>Nurse Nancy said she and Jodie</i>
<i>would do more than just eat dinner.</i>

22:37.880 --> 22:38.916
<i>Will they?</i>

22:39.120 --> 22:41.157
<i>Corinne once said</i>
<i>she would kill Peter.</i>

22:41.360 --> 22:42.555
<i>Did she?</i>

22:42.760 --> 22:44.592
<i>Jessica once said</i>
<i>she would kill Peter.</i>

22:44.800 --> 22:46.075
<i>Did she?</i>

22:46.280 --> 22:48.192
<i>Who killed Peter?</i>

22:48.400 --> 22:54.510
<i>These questions and many others</i>
<i>will be answered on</i>
